Package: kerrigand
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Kerrigan is a hybrid cryptocurrency with multi-algo PoW and
 GPU availability network for AI inference. Kerrigan uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Kerrigan Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, kerrigand, and the CLI tool
 kerrigan-cli to interact with the daemon.

