Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Kerrigan is a hybrid cryptocurrency with multi-algo PoW and
 GPU availability network for AI inference. Kerrigan uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Kerrigan Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides Kerrigan-Qt, a GUI for Kerrigan based on Qt.

Package: kerrigan-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone transaction tool
 Kerrigan is a hybrid cryptocurrency with multi-algo PoW and
 GPU availability network for AI inference. Kerrigan uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Kerrigan Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides kerrigan-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a kerrigan daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.
